<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,z.StartDT ,z.StopDT ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.TargetAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.ActualAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.ActualAF_Oz - z.TargetAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty_Error' ,isnull( (z.ActualAF_Oz - z.TargetAF_Oz) / nullif(z.TargetAF_Oz, 0), 0) as 'TargetAF_ErrorPct' ,dbo.GetLoadDescription(fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID) as 'LoadDescription' ,hr.RecipeName ,he.LocationName as 'MixEquipmentName' ,hfp.FeedingPeriodName ,usr.UserID as 'UserName' ,cmp.CompanyName ,z.IngCount ,z.IngLoaded ,MixIsComplete = convert(bit, case when z.IngLoaded = z.IngCount then 1 else 0 end) ,MixIsPartial = CONVERT(bit, case when z.IngLoaded > 0 and z.IngLoaded < z.IngCount then 1 else 0 end) ,MixIsMissing = CONVERT(bit, case when z.IngCount > 0 and z.IngLoaded = 0 then 1 else 0 end) from ( select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID --,first_mi.TransactionDT as 'StartDT' --,dateadd(second, last_drop.DurationSeconds, last_drop.TransactionDT) as 'StopDT' ,case when map.CreatedDT is null or map.CreatedDT > DATEADD(second, -first_mi.DurationSeconds, first_mi.TransactionDT) then DATEADD(second, -first_mi.DurationSeconds, first_mi.TransactionDT) else map.CreatedDT end as StartDT ,last_drop.TransactionDT as 'StopDT' ,TargetAF_Oz = (select SUM(mi.TargetAFOz) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi where mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID) ,ActualAF_Oz = (select SUM( case when mi.Sequence = 0 and ing.AllowWeighback = 1 and it.UnitQuantity = 0 then mi.TargetAFOz else it.UnitQuantity end ) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID join Ingredient ing on ing.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID where mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID) ,IngCount = (select COUNT(1) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction fsmi left join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID left join RecipeInstruction ri on ri.RecipeInstructionGID = fsmi.RecipeInstructionGID where fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID and fsmi.InventoryItemGID is not null and fsmi.SourceLocationGID is not null and case when it.InventoryTransactionGID is null and ri.Inactive = 1 and ri.ModifiedDT <= fsmi.ModifiedDT then 0 else 1 end = 1) ,IngLoaded = (select COUNT(1) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction fsmi join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID where fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID and fsmi.InventoryItemGID is not null and fsmi.SourceLocationGID is not null) from FeedingScheduleMix fsm
outer apply (select top 1 CreatedDT from FeedingScheduleMixMap map where map.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID) map
outer apply (select top 1 it.* from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID where mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID order by mi.Sequence) first_mi
outer apply (select top 1 drop_trans.* from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm2 on fsm2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID cross apply (select top 1 it.TransactionDT, it.DurationSeconds, row_num = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by it.TransactionSourceGID order by it.TransactionDT) from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID order by row_num desc) drop_trans where fsm2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID
) last_drop
) z join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = z.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join Recipe rec on rec.RecipeGID = coalesce(fsm.ActualRecipeGID, fsm.PlanRecipeGID) left join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = rec.CompanyGID outer apply (select top 1 hr.* from HistoryRecipe hr where hr.RecipeGID = rec.RecipeGID and hr.CreatedDT <= coalesce(z.StartDT, fs.InstanceDate)) hr outer apply (select top 1 he.* from HistoryLocation he where he.LocationGID = coalesce(fsm.ActualLocationGID, fsm.LocationGID) and he.CreatedDT <= coalesce(z.StartDT, fs.InstanceDate)) he outer apply (select top 1 hfp.* from HistoryFeedingPeriod hfp where hfp.FeedingPeriodGID = fs.FeedingPeriodGID and hfp.CreatedDT <= coalesce(z.StartDT, fs.InstanceDate)) hfp left join [User] usr on usr.UserGID = fsm.ByUserGID union all select ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleMixGID, convert(date, mf.CreatedDT) as ReportDate, dateadd(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as StartDT, it.TransactionDT as StopDT, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as TargetAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as ActualAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as TargetAF_MQty_Error, case when it.TargetUnitQuantity = 0 then 0 else it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity / it.TargetUnitQuantity end as TargetAF_ErrorPct, ii.InventoryItemName as LoadDescription, '' as RecipeName, l.LocationName as MixEquipmentName, 'SYSTEM' as FeedingPeriodName, u.UserID as UserName, cmp.CompanyName, 1 as IngCount, 1 as IngLoaded, convert(bit, 1) as MixIsComplete, 0 as MixIsPartial, 0 as MixIsMissing from ManualFeeding mf join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mf.ManualFeedingGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join EquipmentLocation el on el.LocationGID = l.LocationGID join Equipment eq on eq.EquipmentGID = el.EquipmentGID join EquipmentType eqt on eqt.EquipmentTypeGID = eq.EquipmentTypeGID and eqt.OperationType <> 2 join [User] u on u.UserGID = mf.UserGID ) mixsum where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>

-- Mix Sum select z.* ,c.CompanyName ,dbo.GetLoadDescription(z.FeedingScheduleMixGID) as 'LoadDescription' ,u.UserID as 'UserName' ,r.RecipeName ,le.LocationName as 'Equipment' from ( select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.PlanRecipeGID ,fsm.ByUserGID ,fsm.LocationGID ,MIN(fs.InstanceDate) as 'ReportDate' ,MIN(CONVERT(datetime, convert(time, it.TransactionDT))) as 'StartTime' ,MAX(CONVERT(datetime, convert(time, it.TransactionDT))) as 'StopTime' --,MIN(CONVERT(datetime, convert(date, dbo.GetInventoryTransactionReportDT(it.InventoryTransactionGID)))) as 'ReportDate2' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(mi.TargetAFOz), 54) as 'TargetAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(it.UnitQuantity), 54) as 'AFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(it.UnitQuantity) - SUM(mi.TargetAFOz), 54) as 'TargetAFLbsError' ,ISNULL( (SUM(it.UnitQuantity) - SUM(mi.TargetAFOz)) / NULLIF(SUM(mi.TargetAFOz), 0), 0) as 'TargetAFErrorPct'
from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi with (nolock) join InventoryTransaction it with (nolock) on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm with (nolock) on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs with (nolock) on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID where it.TransactionType = 4 group by fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.PlanRecipeGID ,fsm.ByUserGID ,fsm.LocationGID ) z
join Recipe r on r.RecipeGID = z.PlanRecipeGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = z.ByUserGID join Location le with (nolock) on le.LocationGID = z.LocationGID join Company c with (nolock) on c.CompanyGID = r.CompanyGID where (1=1)

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select z.* from (select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.ByUserGID ,c.CompanyName ,fs.InstanceDate as ReportDate ,u.UserID as UserName ,mi.Sequence ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then 'Delay' else coalesce(hii.InventoryItemName, ii.InventoryItemName) end as Ingredient ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then '' else coalesce(hfl.LocationName, sl.LocationName, 'UNKNOWN') end as Location ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then (select min(SnapshotDT) from WeightSnapshotEntry wse join WeightSnapshot ws on ws.WeightSnapshotGID = wse.WeightSnapshotGID where ws.SourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID) else DATEADD(SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) end as StartDT ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then (select max(SnapshotDT) from WeightSnapshotEntry wse join WeightSnapshot ws on ws.WeightSnapshotGID = wse.WeightSnapshotGID where ws.SourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID) else it.TransactionDT end as StopDT ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then DATEADD(second, mi.ActualDurationSeconds, '1900-01-01') else it.TransactionDT - DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) end as ElapsedTime ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then ri.Quantity * 60 else dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, c.MediumMeasurementType) end as TargetAF_MQty ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then mi.ActualDurationSeconds else dbo.GetMeasurementValue(case when mi.Sequence = 0 and ing.AllowWeighback = 1 and it.UnitQuantity = 0 then mi.TargetAFOz else it.UnitQuantity end, c.MediumMeasurementType) end as ActualAF_MQty ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then abs(mi.ActualDurationSeconds - ri.Quantity * 60) else dbo.GetMeasurementValue(case when mi.Sequence = 0 and ing.AllowWeighback = 1 and it.UnitQuantity = 0 then mi.TargetAFOz else it.UnitQuantity end - mi.TargetAFOz, c.MediumMeasurementType) end as TargetAF_MQty_Error ,case when ra.RecipeActionType = 1 then case when ri.Quantity = 0 then 0 else (mi.ActualDurationSeconds - ri.Quantity * 60) / (ri.Quantity * 60) end else isnull((case when mi.Sequence = 0 and ing.AllowWeighback = 1 and it.UnitQuantity = 0 then mi.TargetAFOz else it.UnitQuantity end - mi.TargetAFOz) / nullif(mi.TargetAFOz, 0), 0) end as TargetErrorPct ,DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) - o.LastTransactionDT as TimeSinceLast ,IsMissing = convert(bit, case when it.InventoryTransactionGID is null and (ri.Inactive = 1 and ri.ModifiedDT > mi.ModifiedDT) then 1 else 0 end) ,IsFed = CONVERT(bit, case when it.InventoryTransactionGID is null and mi.ActualDurationSeconds = 0 then 0 else 1 end) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi with (nolock) left join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = mi.InventoryItemGID left join Ingredient ing on ing.InventoryItemGID = ii.InventoryItemGID left join Location sl on sl.LocationGID = mi.SourceLocationGID left join InventoryTransaction it with (nolock) on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID left join HistoryInventoryItem hii with (nolock) on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID left join HistoryLocation hfl with (nolock) on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm with (nolock) on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs with (nolock) on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingPeriod fp with (nolock) on fp.FeedingPeriodGID = fs.FeedingPeriodGID join Company c with (nolock) on c.CompanyGID = fp.CompanyGID left join [User] u with (nolock) on u.UserGID = fsm.ByUserGID left join RecipeInstruction ri on ri.RecipeInstructionGID = mi.RecipeInstructionGID left join RecipeAction ra on ra.RecipeActionGID = ri.RecipeActionGID outer apply (select max(TransactionDT) as LastTransactionDT from (select case when ra2.RecipeActionType = 1 then (select max(SnapshotDT) from WeightSnapshotEntry wse join WeightSnapshot ws on ws.WeightSnapshotGID = wse.WeightSnapshotGID where ws.SourceGID = mi2.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID) else it2.TransactionDT end as TransactionDT from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi2 left join RecipeInstruction ri2 on ri2.RecipeInstructionGID = mi2.RecipeInstructionGID left join RecipeAction ra2 on ra2.RecipeActionGID = ri2.RecipeActionGID left join InventoryTransaction it2 on mi2.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID = it2.TransactionSourceGID where mi2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID and mi2.Sequence < mi.Sequence) os ) o ) z union all select ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleMixGID, ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleGID, u.UserGID as ByUserGID, cmp.CompanyName, convert(date, mf.CreatedDT) as ReportDate, u.UserID as UserName, 0 as Sequence, ii.InventoryItemName as Ingredient, l2.LocationName as Location, dateadd(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as StartDT, it.TransactionDT as StopDT, it.TransactionDT - DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as ElapsedTime, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as TargetAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as ActualAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as TargetAF_MQty_Error, case when it.TargetUnitQuantity = 0 then 0 else it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity / it.TargetUnitQuantity end as TargetErrorPct, null as TimeSinceLast, 0 as IsMissing, 1 as IsFed from ManualFeeding mf join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mf.ManualFeedingGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join EquipmentLocation el on el.LocationGID = l.LocationGID join Equipment eq on eq.EquipmentGID = el.EquipmentGID join EquipmentType eqt on eqt.EquipmentTypeGID = eq.EquipmentTypeGID and eqt.OperationType <> 2 join [User] u on u.UserGID = mf.UserGID join Location l2 on l2.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID ) mixing where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement: -- MixIngredients select * from ( select z.* from (select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.ByUserGID ,c.CompanyName ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,u.UserID as 'UserName' ,mi.Sequence ,hii.InventoryItemName as 'Ingredient' ,hfl.LocationName as 'Location' --,convert(datetime, convert(date, dbo.GetInventoryTransactionReportDT(it.InventoryTransactionGID))) as 'ReportDate' ,convert(datetime, convert(time, it.TransactionDT)) as 'StartTime' ,convert(datetime, convert(time, dateadd(second, it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT))) as 'StopTime' ,convert(datetime, convert(time, dateadd(second, it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) - it.TransactionDT)) as 'ElapsedTime' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, 54) as 'TargetAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, 54) as 'AFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz, 54) as 'TargetAFLbsError' ,isnull( (it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz) / nullif(mi.TargetAFOz, 0), 0) as 'TargetAFErrorPct' ,convert(datetime, convert(time, it.TransactionDT - o.LastTransactionDT)) as 'TimeSinceLast' from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi with (nolock) join InventoryTransaction it with (nolock) on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii with (nolock) on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID join HistoryLocation hfl with (nolock) on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm with (nolock) on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs with (nolock) on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingPeriod fp with (nolock) on fp.FeedingPeriodGID = fs.FeedingPeriodGID join Company c with (nolock) on c.CompanyGID = fp.CompanyGID left join [User] u with (nolock) on u.UserGID = fsm.ByUserGID outer apply (select MAX(it2.TransactionDT) as 'LastTransactionDT' from InventoryTransaction it2 join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi2 on mi2.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID = it2.TransactionSourceGID where mi2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID and mi2.Sequence < mi.Sequence) o ) z) mixing where (1=1)

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID ,fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,DropSequence = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID order by drop_trans.StartDT) ,hl.LocationName ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,drop_trans.StartDT ,drop_trans.StopDT ,convert(time, drop_trans.StopDT - drop_trans.StartDT) as 'ElapsedTime' ,drop_trans.PartialDropNumber ,drop_trans.PartialDropCount ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsd.PlanAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'PlanAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(isnull(adjustedAF.AdjustedAF_Oz, fsd.PlanAFOz), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AdjustedAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(drop_trans.DropAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(drop_trans.DropAF_Oz - isnull(adjustedAF.AdjustedAF_Oz, fsd.PlanAFOz), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AdjustedAF_MQty_Error' ,isnull( (drop_trans.DropAF_Oz - adjustedAF.AdjustedAF_Oz) / nullif(drop_trans.DropAF_Oz, 0), 0) as 'AdjustedErrorPct' ,usr.UserID as 'UserName' ,cmp.CompanyName ,PenCount = (select top 1 pcc.[Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = pn.PenGID and pcc.InventoryItemType = 3 and pcc.CreatedDT <= drop_trans.StartDT order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) ,hfl.LocationName as 'EquipmentName' ,IsPartial = convert(bit, case when drop_trans.PartialDropNumber = drop_trans.PartialDropCount then 0 else 1 end) from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join Location dl on dl.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = dl.CompanyGID
cross apply (select DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as 'StartDT' ,it.TransactionDT as 'StopDT' ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,SUM(it.UnitQuantity) as 'DropAF_Oz' ,PartialDropNumber = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by it.TransactionSourceGID order by it.TransactionDT) ,PartialDropCount = COUNT(1) over(partition by it.TransactionSourceGID) from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID group by it.TransactionSourceGID, it.TransactionDT, it.DurationSeconds, it.FromHistoryLocationGID) drop_trans left join [User] usr on usr.UserGID = fsd.ByUserGID left join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID left join HistoryLocation hfl on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = drop_trans.FromHistoryLocationGID outer apply (select top 1 fsda.* from FeedingScheduleDropAdjustment fsda where fsda.FeedingScheduleDropGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID order by fsda.AdjustmentDT desc) fsda
outer apply (select case when drop_trans.PartialDropNumber = drop_trans.PartialDropCount then fsda.AdjustedAFOz else drop_trans.DropAF_Oz end as 'AdjustedAF_Oz') adjustedAF outer apply (select top 1 hl.* from HistoryLocation hl where hl.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID and hl.CreatedDT <= drop_trans.StartDT order by hl.CreatedDT desc) hl union all select ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleMixGID, ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleLoadGID, ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleDropGID, 1 as DropSequence, l2.LocationName, convert(date, mf.CreatedDT) as ReportDate, dateadd(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as StartDT, it.TransactionDT as StopDT, it.TransactionDT - DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as ElapsedTime, 0 as PartialDropNumber, 0 as PartialDropCount, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as PlanAF_MQty, 0 as AdjustedAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as ActualAF_MQty, 0 as AdjustedAF_MQty_Error, 0 as AdjustedErrorPct, u.UserID as UserName, cmp.CompanyName, isnull(pcc.[Count], 0) as PenCount, l.LocationName as EquipmentName, 0 as IsPartial from ManualFeeding mf join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mf.ManualFeedingGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID join EquipmentLocation el on el.LocationGID = l.LocationGID join Equipment eq on eq.EquipmentGID = el.EquipmentGID join [User] u on u.UserGID = mf.UserGID join Location l2 on l2.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID and l2.LocationType in (0, 1) left join Pen p on p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID outer apply (select top 1 [Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = p.PenGID and pcc.CreatedDT <= it.TransactionDT order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) pcc ) drp where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
--LoadDrops select drp.* from (select z.* ,c.CompanyName ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,htl.LocationName as 'Location' ,u.UserID as 'UserName' ,hfl.LocationName as 'Equipment' ,(select top 1 pcc.[Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = p.PenGID and pcc.InventoryItemType = 3 and pcc.CreatedDT <= z.StartDT order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) as 'PenCount' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsda.AdjustedAFOz, 54) as 'AdjAFLbs' ,z.AFLbs - dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsda.AdjustedAFOz, 54) as 'AdjAFError' ,ISNULL( (z.AFOz - fsda.AdjustedAFOz) / nullif(fsda.AdjustedAFOz, 0), 0) as 'AdjAFErrorPct' from (select fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID ,fsd.ByUserGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleGID ,it.ToLocationGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,it.FromLocationGID ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,c.CompanyGID ,fsd.Sequence ,SUM(it.UnitQuantity) as 'AFOz' ,MIN(it.TransactionDT) as 'StartDT' ,MIN(it.TransactionDT) as 'TransactionDT' ,CONVERT(datetime, CONVERT(time, MIN(it.TransactionDT))) as 'StartTime' ,CONVERT(datetime, CONVERT(time, MAX(dateadd(second, it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT)))) as 'StopTime' --,CONVERT(datetime, CONVERT(date, MAX(it.TransactionDT))) as 'ReportDate' -- <<<<< HACK: for initial testing only! ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(it.UnitQuantity), 54) as 'AFLbs' from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd with (nolock) join InventoryTransaction it with (nolock) on it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl with (nolock) on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm with (nolock) on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs with (nolock) on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingPeriod fp with (nolock) on fp.FeedingPeriodGID = fs.FeedingPeriodGID join Company c with (nolock) on c.CompanyGID = fp.CompanyGID where it.TransactionType = 1 or it.TransactionType = 4
group by c.CompanyGID ,fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID ,fsd.ByUserGID ,fsd.Sequence ,fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,it.ToLocationGID ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,it.FromLocationGID ) z join Company c with (nolock) on c.CompanyGID = z.CompanyGID join HistoryLocation htl on htl.HistoryLocationGID = z.ToHistoryLocationGID join FeedingSchedule fs with (nolock) on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = z.FeedingScheduleGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = z.ByUserGID join HistoryLocation hfl on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = z.FromHistoryLocationGID left join Pen p with (nolock) on p.LocationGID = z.ToLocationGID outer apply (select top 1 fsda.* from FeedingScheduleDropAdjustment fsda where fsda.FeedingScheduleDropGID = z.FeedingScheduleDropGID order by fsda.AdjustmentDT desc) fsda ) drp where (1=1)

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID ,LoadSequence = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID order by load_trans.StartDT) ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,load_trans.StartDT ,load_trans.StopDT ,convert(time, load_trans.StopDT - load_trans.StartDT) as 'ElapsedTime' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(TargetLoadAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(load_trans.LoadAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(load_trans.LoadAF_Oz - TargetLoadAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as Error ,isnull( (load_trans.LoadAF_Oz - TargetLoadAF_Oz) / nullif(load_trans.LoadAF_Oz, 0), 0) as ErrorPct ,usr.UserID as 'UserName' ,cmp.CompanyName ,hfl.LocationName as MixEquipment ,htl.LocationName as DropEquipment from FeedingScheduleLoad fsl join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join Location ll on ll.LocationGID = fsl.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ll.CompanyGID
cross apply (select DATEADD(second, -max(it.DurationSeconds), max(it.TransactionDT)) as 'StartDT' ,max(it.TransactionDT) as 'StopDT' ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,SUM(it.UnitQuantity) as LoadAF_Oz ,SUM(it.TargetUnitQuantity) as TargetLoadAF_Oz from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionSourceGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID group by it.TransactionSourceGID, it.FromHistoryLocationGID, it.ToHistoryLocationGID) load_trans left join [User] usr on usr.UserGID = fsl.ByUserGID left join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = fsl.LocationGID left join HistoryLocation hfl on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = load_trans.FromHistoryLocationGID left join HistoryLocation htl on htl.HistoryLocationGID = load_trans.ToHistoryLocationGID union all select ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleMixGID, ManualFeedingGID as FeedingScheduleLoadGID, 1 as LoadSequence, convert(date, mf.CreatedDT) as ReportDate, dateadd(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as StartDT, it.TransactionDT as StopDT, it.TransactionDT - DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as ElapsedTime, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as TargetAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as ActualAF_MQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as Error, case when it.TargetUnitQuantity = 0 then 0 else it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity / it.TargetUnitQuantity end as ErrorPct, u.UserID as UserName, cmp.CompanyName, l.LocationName as MixEquipmentName, l2.LocationName as DropEquipmentName from ManualFeeding mf join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mf.ManualFeedingGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join EquipmentLocation el on el.LocationGID = l.LocationGID join [User] u on u.UserGID = mf.UserGID join Location l2 on l2.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID join EquipmentLocation el2 on el2.LocationGID = l2.LocationGID ) ld where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
